Manage evaluation runs

Usage:
  agentclash run [command]

Available Commands:
  agents      List agents in a run
  create      Create and submit an evaluation run
  events      Stream live run events via SSE
  get         Get run details
  list        List runs in the workspace
  open        Open the run replay in the web UI
  ranking     Get run ranking and composite scores
  scorecard   Get agent scorecard
  show        Human-readable summary of a run

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for run

Global Flags:
      --api-url string     API base URL (overrides config)
      --json               Output in JSON format
      --no-color           Disable color output
      --non-interactive    Disable interactive prompts (also honored: CI=true, AGENTCLASH_NON_INTERACTIVE=1, --json, no TTY)
  -o, --output string      Output format: table, json, yaml
  -q, --quiet              Suppress non-essential output
  -v, --verbose            Enable debug output on stderr
  -w, --workspace string   Workspace ID (overrides config)
      --yes                Skip confirmation prompts

Use "agentclash run [command] --help" for more information about a command.
